cu.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value -1 will cause cell ID validation failure as NR cell IDs must be non-negative.

du.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value -1 will cause cell ID validation failure as NR cell IDs must be non-negative.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為負值 -1 會導致細胞 ID 驗證失敗，因為 NR 細胞 ID 必須為非負數。
